FSRI: Dimensions: 98.12 x 98.34 x 39.55 mm; with frame and grid

A few seconds prior to ignition the laminate inflated, then popped violently, possibly affecting mass data. The flames extinguished within 5 seconds of ignition. The spark ignitor was reinserted, and reignition occurred immediately. Throughout this time, the inflation of the laminate pushed the wire grid upwards, approaching the spark ignitor.
